docs {
  # Update Vendor (Partial)

  Partially updates a vendor. Only provided fields are modified.

  ## Path Parameters

  | Param | Description |
  |-------|-------------|
  | id | Vendor identifier |

  ## Request Body

  Include only the fields you want to update:

  ```json
  {
    "description": "Updated description"
  }
  ```

  ## Response

  Returns the complete updated vendor object.

  ## Error Responses

  - `404 Not Found`: Vendor does not exist
  - `400 Bad Request`: Invalid JSON body
}
